Author: AmbiguousCat
Text: It’s also prescriptionless from India so you can order online. It’s a decently safe drug. Not so jittery like caffiene or adderall. Like I had a good nights rest despite getting maybe three hours of sleep. The effects are not as noticeable like, I just feel good and awake and a little more focused.

Author: relapseandrecovery
Text: After googling the uses, I feel like I could get a prescription for this at some point. I'm tired all the time and some doctors hand out prescriptions like crazy. I'm interested to try now
